dc_description_s: This line data layer represents trails for Green County, Wisconsin in 2017. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Green_Trails_2017.gdb. [To be used by Green County Sheriff's Dispatcher's through their third party E911 dispatching and reporting system created by Spillman Technologies. Data created in conjunction with State E911 update grant. Features were derived from a variety of sources including deeds, descriptions, subdivision maps, certified survey maps, easements, and right of way maps. These source materials were of varying scale and date. This coverage provides a representation of the geometry and topology of tax parcels within the County, and is suitable as a reference layer within the County's GIS.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For complete metadata documentation please visit http://www.co.green.wi.gov/localgov_departments_details.asp?deptid=115&locid=148 .This data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2017. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2016. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2017.[DATE OF 2017 IS ATTACHED TO THIS DATASET'S NAME, BUT THIS DATASET MOST LIKELYIS NOT UP-TO-DATE. PRESUMABLY GREEN COUNTY HAS DONE SOME MAINTENANCE OF THISDATASET, BUT THE SOURCE(S) MAY ACTUALLY BE UNKNOWN.]
